            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x6d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I don't mind either. Thinking alone all the time is bad for efficiency, anyway."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yay, thanks! To tell the truth... I've always wanted to ask you something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "You look similar... Are you siblings?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Siblings...? It's hard to explain..."
